latestIgtvVideos.title: Double Cleansing ft. @forestessentials
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi babes! Please leave your skincare concerns/questions in the comments below! 
.
The benefit of double cleansing is that firstly, the CLEANSER will break down any makeup, remove dirt and excess oils from the day and clean your skin. The second cleanser will address your particular skin type or concern and should have ingredients to hydrate, smooth or exfoliate and treat acne.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Cleaning My Makeup Brushes ✌︎︎
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys! We have all the time in the world- so why not indulge in sanitising our makeup brushes and other tools? ☞︎ All you need is a mild shampoo, water, cleansing mat/ mug and a towel. ☞︎ Make sure to air dry them overnight rather than blow drying. ☞︎ Please clean them every week to avoid germs, infections and rashes 
Lots of love, Sim ♡︎
__
